dataLabel: Get 10  Items from the zika corpus
queryMap:
SPARQL '''PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>

SELECT * WHERE {?item wdt:P921 wd:Q202864 ;} LIMIT 10'''@START
